# Eloquent JavaScript Handbook

Welcome to the Eloquent JavaScript Handbook (4th Edition) repository! This repository is dedicated to providing a comprehensive guide, including tips, tricks, exercises, projects, and additional resources, to enhance your learning experience with the book _Eloquent JavaScript_.

## Table of Contents

- [Eloquent JavaScript Handbook](#eloquent-javascript-handbook)
